text: Wendy Nicholls (born 22 May 1937) is an Australian gymnast. She competed in five events at the 1956 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1937 births Category:Living people Category:Australian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Australia Category:Gymnasts at the 1956 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
